current.magic_text1: TERMS & CONDITIONS - Can I return my item?
current.magic_txt1:
Please read the Returns Policy before returning a product to The WOD Life.
Please download and print your Return Authorisation Form HERE. Fill out the form with all necessary information and return to the address listed.

Please read the Processes and Policies below.
Any issues, please contact us.
current.magic_text2: RETURNS POLICY - What's your policy on returns?
current.magic_txt2:
The WOD Life takes it’s products and customer service seriously. We are committed to ensuring you are satisfied with your purchase. If there is ever an issue with our products or services provided, please get in contact with us. We will take care of this together with you to ensure you are satisfied.

Please select carefully as there are no returns, exchanges or refunds provided on Nutritional or Supplement Products, Books and Media.

No returns, exchanges or refunds can be provided on items returned to The WOD Life in a used condition, or outside our terms and conditions.

Please note that we will be only be providing a refund by the methods available to us at the time of your return. This may involve Bank Deposit, PayPal, Credit Card Reversal or Store Credit. Please allow up to 7-14 days for refunds or credits to be processed.
current.magic_text3: RETURNS PROCESS - How do I return an item?
current.magic_txt3:
• If you decide you are not satisfied with your purchase you have 100 days from receipt of purchase to return and obtain a refund.
  • You must use the download, print and complete the Return Authorisation HERE to begin the Returns Process.
  • Please ensure you include Your Name, Order Number, Shipping Address and details for return or exchange. It is important you complete the Return Authorisation requirements, with all details to assist in the smooth process of your request.
  • Please include the Return Authorisation Form with your product in the return package.
  • You are responsible for the return of the product, in an unused, as new condition.
  • You must select the appropriate method of shipping to return the product. We recommend using Australia Post Registered Mail, so you are able to track your return and confirmed we have received it.
  • Upon receipt of the returned items, we will refund the cost of the items or provide a store credit. We will not refund the cost of shipping.
  • Where a replacement item is currently out of stock, a refund or store credit will be issued at our discretion.
  • Please allow 7-14 Business Days from receipt of returned goods, for your return to be processed.
  • We will contact you as soon as the Return or Exchange has been processed by our returns department. Please do not email requesting updates as this will further delay the process.
  • Returns Address is as follows:
The WOD Life
C/O – Returns Department
Unit 4 / 135 Mooringe Avenue
Camden Park
South Australia
Australia
5038
current.magic_text4: DAMAGED OR FAULTY GOODS - My items are damaged or faulty, what do I do?
current.magic_txt4:
If your gear becomes damaged or faulty after use, The WOD Life will work together with you to resolve the issue. If your gear has been used according to it’s intended use and are still within the returns period, we will work together with you to organise a replacement or a refund.
We will not replace or refund gear that is damaged through incorrect use, outside the terms of use or through natural wear and tear.
If your gear does not arrive in original condition or there is a fault, we will work together with you to ensure you are provided with what you purchased. Please contact us with your order number and we will organise a replacement.
current.magic_text5: INCORRECT ITEMS RECEIVED - The correct item wasn't received, what do I do?
current.magic_txt5:
We acknowledge that at times, there may be mixed up items that are received. We will work with you immediately to ensure your correct item is received.
Please contact us with your order order number, the incorrect item and we will resolve this for you.

settings.text: We're here to help you discover what you're capable of. From the latest performance apparel, freshest footwear and quality gear, to the latest in equipment. We have everything you need for your first workout to your next competition, all in one place.

settings.title: WHAT IS TWL?
settings.text: A destination to help you discover what you're capable of. Providing everyone - from the beginner signing up to the gym to the athlete throwing down in their next competition - with high quality products, expert advice and motivation all in one place. To inch closer to your limits, break them, and go beyond what you thought was possible.
settings.code: • Welcome to The WOD Life. The Home of Training.

settings.title: TWL core values
settings.code:
• Community. Because we're part of it. We aim to bolster the community through putting on events, sharing advice and offering a wide range of products that we'd use ourselves.
  • Quality. To be the best, you need the best. That's why we only sell products we believe in or would use ourselves. We understand that you, our customer has concerns, wants and needs and we aim to recommend products that will solve, aid and benefit your training.
  • Sweat. We believe that training isn't something to just tick off the list or is some sort of obligation. It's a lifestyle. We value the motivation it takes to start training, roll out of bed for an early morning workout, and the strength it takes to bounce back after injury.
  • The impossible is possible. There is no such word as can't in our book. We believe edges are made to go over, personal bests are made to be broken. That training is the gateway to a stronger, more fulfilled life.

settings.title: Get in touch
settings.text: Got a question? Want to collaborate? Looking for a job at one of the fastest growing companies in the training segment? Contact us at support@thewodlife.com.au. In the meantime, join us on one of the many online platforms.

settings.qusetion: Who is The WOD Life?
settings.answer: • The WOD Life is a Registered Australian Business with Australian Business Number 54 114 453 116. To find out more, feel free to check out our 'About' page.

settings.qusetion: Do you have a real life store? Can I come in and look at your gear? Can I pick up my order at your store?
settings.answer: • Unfortunately not. At this point in time, we do not have a retail location. Our website is a one stop shop, where you can sit back, relax and enjoy browsing at your own leisure!

settings.qusetion: Where are you located?
settings.answer: • We are located in Australia. Look out for us at an event near you!

settings.qusetion: What are your trading hours?
settings.answer: • We are an online store, so technically 24 hours a day, 7 days a week! However if you have a particular query please contact us and a member of our team will get aim to respond within 24-48 hours.

settings.qusetion: My Afterpay was declined, what's wrong?
settings.answer:
• The Afterpay payment option is managed by Afterpay directly, so we have no control over the acceptance or rejection of payments.

    There are a few reasons why a payment can be declined with Afterpay:

    - Your first payment amount must be available at the time of purchase - even if you have nothing to pay today
    - Your Afterpay account has overdue payments owing
    - The Afterpay risk management department has declined your payment
    - For any questions regarding your Afterpay payment please contact Afterpay.

    For more details, you can get in touch with Afterpay.

settings.qusetion: Do you ship internationally?
settings.answer:
• The WOD Life is committed to getting our products to our customers. We now can provide International Shipping to customers located throughout the world. If you have a special request, feel free to contact us. 
  • The WOD Life is not to be held responsible for any customs duties or clearance payments at the receiving country. These clearance fees and customs duties are all unique to the country and are up to the customer to make payment.

settings.qusetion: When will my order arrive?
settings.answer:
• As soon as you place an order, you will receive an order confirmation email. If you did not receive this, please check your Junk Mail Folder.
  • Please allow us to pick, pack and ship  your order within 24-48 hours on business days. When your order is shipped, you will receive a subsequent confirmation with all shipping information and details.
  • If you would like to check the current status of your order, please click on ORDER STATUS.

settings.qusetion: How long will my order take to arrive? What are the shipping times?
settings.answer:
• As a guide, Domestic orders are shipped via standard Australia Post and arrive between 5-7 Business Days to all major centres excluding Darwin (Please allow 1-2 extra days). Customers orders can arrive before this, however this timeframe is provided as a guide only.
  • For Express Orders, please allow 1-2 Business Days for your order to arrive in all major centres excluding Darwin (Please allow 1-2 extra days).
  • For International Orders including New Zealand, please allow 4-7 Business Days for your items to arrive. As we post to all corners of the globe, each order is unique and the time frame can range.

settings.qusetion: How much is shipping?
settings.answer: • Shipping costs are calculated based on the weight, size and shipping location. For accurate shipping costs, please add all of your items to your CART. Click on your CART, enter your state/territory, country and zip/postal code to get a real time shipping quote.

settings.qusetion: Can I pick up my order from the store?
settings.answer: • At this point in time, we do not have a retail location so pick ups are unavailable.

settings.qusetion: What is my tracking number?
settings.answer:
• Due to the volume orders, The WOD Life is unable to provide a tracking number for those orders 500g and under. In all other circumstances, tracking numbers will be provided to you in the shipping confirmation email where possible.
  • If you have ordered via Express Post, once the item has shipped, your tracking number, should be then included in your shipping confirmation email.
  • If you have not received a shipping confirmation email, please check your Junk Mail Folder before contacting us.

settings.qusetion: I just realised I ordered the wrong colour/size/quantity/product. What do I do?
settings.answer:
• Once your order has been placed, it has begun to be processed and no amendments or cancellations can be made. We are not able to combine orders or make any changes during this time.
  • If you require additional products added to your original order, we recommend that you place another order to ensure that you do not miss out on your item, due to the fluctuations in available stock.
  • You can always test your luck and contact us, we will see if it is possible to accommodate your change.

settings.qusetion: My item is the wrong size / style / colour and I need to return it. What do I do?
settings.answer: • The WOD Life is committed to ensuring that all customers are satisfied and we offer a 100 Day Return Policy. For all returns policies and procedures please visit the RETURNS PAGE. All information on the returns process, our terms and conditions are featured here.

settings.qusetion: I've sent my returns items back, have you received them yet?
settings.answer: • Please review our returns page for our policies and procedures. When The WOD Life has processed your return, exchange or refund we will be in contact with you via the details provided in the Returns Authorisation Form.

settings.qusetion: I want to return an item, but I have lost my original invoice?
settings.answer: • No problems, please go to the RETURNS PAGE to download the RETURNS AUTHORISATION form. Fill in the details of this form, send it in with your item and we will process accordingly.

settings.qusetion: Does The WOD Life do buys or custom affiliate orders?
settings.answer: • Definitely!!! The WOD Life has great relationships with some of the biggest and best brands around the Functional Fitness market, so if you are after a group buy or a larger order for your affiliate contact us at support@thewodlife.com.au with the product and reference and we will work together with you to make it happen.

settings.qusetion: Do you offer Wholesale Pricing?
settings.answer: • The WOD Life has established a wholesale program, geared towards Affiliates and Gym Owners. This program assists these affiliates and gym owners to access bulk rates for specific purchases. If you are interested in establishing an affiliate/wholesale account, please sign up at our AFFILIATE PAGE.

settings.qusetion: Do  you offer special deals for Affiliates?
settings.answer: • If you are interested in an affiliate/wholesale account, please sign up at our AFFILIATE PAGE.

settings.qusetion: I'm looking to open a new affiliate, how do we partner with The WOD Life?
settings.answer: • The WOD Life is always looking to assist new affiliates. Please do yourself a favour and register for the AFFILIATE Program. Any information can be sent directly through to affiliates@thewodlife.com.au

settings.qusetion: When will  you be getting my item back in stock? Can you let me know when you get my item back in stock?
settings.answer:
• Due to the popularity, certain items go out of stock from time to time. On the relevant product page, please select your size/style/colour/type that is currently out of stock.
  • Please then put your email address in the notifications field. Once your email is input, please click "Email when available". As soon as the item comes back in stock, you will then receive an automatic notification.

settings.qusetion: What size should I order?
settings.answer: • We realise that everyone has a difference preference on how they would like an item to fit. We have provided size charts and size guides for as many items as possible on our site. Just check the product listing and photos for a size guide. If you are after specific guidance or a chart isn't available - get in contact with us.

settings.qusetion: Where is your size guide?
settings.answer: • Please check the size guide on the specific product's page. We have many different products from many different suppliers, so sizing across products can vary.

settings.qusetion: What if The WOD Life does not stock a product I am interested in?

settings.qusetion: Will The WOD Life sponsor my event?
settings.answer:
• The WOD Life is actively involved in the community. Unfortunately it is not possible to sponsor every event. If you believe you have a worthy event, please consider the following criteria:
  • 1. Are you or your affiliate a customer of The WOD Life?
  • 2. Do you use our gear and believe in The WOD Life?
  • 3. When and what is your event?
  • 4. How many people will be attending your event?
  • 5. What support will you be looking for from The WOD Life?

settings.qusetion: Will The WOD Life sponsor me as an athlete?
settings.answer:
• The WOD Life is open to sponsoring specific athletes and ambassadors amongst the community. If you believe you are a worthy candidate, please consider the following criteria
  • 1. Are you a customer of The WOD Life?
  • 2. Do you use our gear and believe in The WOD Life?
  • 3. Do you have a presence within the community?
  • 4. Are you actively involved in sanctioned and unsanctioned CrossFit, Olympic Lifting, Power Lifting, Gymnastics and Functional Fitness events?
